{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Capture Metaball"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 21], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [131, 214], "text": ["Captures points on geometry to metaballs,\nsimilarly to capturing to a bone."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [214, 300], "text": ["By itself, this operator does not affect the geometry. The metaballs are\nnot output."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [300, 589], "text": ["Connect the skin geometry to the first input, and input the paths to the\nmetaball SOPs in the Metaball SOPs parameter. The metaballs must be in\n", {"text": ["primitive groups"], "fullpath": "/model/groups", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/model/groups"}, " . To interactively perform a\ncapture, use the ", {"text": ["Capture Geometry"], "fullpath": "/shelf/capturegeometry", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/capturegeometry"}, " tool\nat the OBJ level."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [589, 742], "text": ["Captured points will have a ", {"text": ["metaCapture"], "type": "code"}, " point attribute containing the\nname of the metaball group that captured the point, and the group\u2019s\nweighting."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [742, 908], "text": ["The density of the metaball where it captured the skin geometry at the\ncapture frame controls how much influence the metaball has when it\ndeforms the skin geometry."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1038, 1070], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/capturegeometry", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/capturegeometry"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "text": ["You can edit the influence of the metaballs on the skin per-group by\nusing the ", {"text": ["Capture Layer Paint SOP"], "fullpath": "/shelf/paintcapturelayer", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/paintcapturelayer"}], "extent": [908, 1038], "container": true, "type": "para"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1101, 1268], "text": ["Paths to the SOPs containing the metaballs. These are typically paths\n        to Muscle SOPs which create a series of metaballs representing a\n        muscle."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Metaball SOPs"], "role": "item", "extent": [1082, 1101], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1287, 1447], "text": ["Frame number at which to compute the capture weighting. This\n        frame will cook slower than other frames due to the\n        weighting computation."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Capture Frame"], "role": "item", "extent": [1268, 1287], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1477, 1523], "text": ["Destroy any existing capture weights."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Destroy Existing Weights"], "role": "item", "extent": [1447, 1477], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1541, 1704], "text": ["If destroy existing weights is off, then this parameter\n        determines the blend factor of the created capture weights\n        with the existing ones."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Blend Factor"], "role": "item", "extent": [1523, 1541], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1727, 1810], "text": ["Whether to visualize the capture weights by coloring the\n        geometry."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Visualize Capture"], "role": "item", "extent": [1704, 1727], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1830, 1942], "text": ["Whether to visualize weights as a single weight, or as multiple colors\n        for all capture regions."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Visualize Type"], "role": "item", "extent": [1810, 1830], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1962, 2069], "text": ["For the single primitive visualize type, this specifies how to map the\n        weights to a color."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Visualize Mode"], "role": "item", "extent": [1942, 1962], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2098, 2218], "text": ["For the multiple primitives visualize type, this specifies the color\n        used for points with zero weights."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Zero Weight Point Color"], "role": "item", "extent": [2069, 2098], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2239, 2275], "text": ["Forces the node to recook."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Force Recapture"], "role": "item", "extent": [2218, 2239], "container": true, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [1070, 1082], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2284, 2308], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/muscle", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/muscle"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2308, 2340], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/deformmuscle"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [2275, 2284], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Captures points on geometry to metaballs,\nsimilarly to capturing to a bone."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "capture, character, metaball", "namespace": null, "internal": "capturemeta", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/capturemeta"}, "title": ["Capture Metaball"]}